data.description: Introducing a Charming Colonial Gem in the Heart of York Suburban Schools! Are you on the hunt for an ideal investment property or a starter home with character and history? Look no further! This adorable and well-maintained historic colonial is your perfect opportunity. Property features a NEWER ROOF, New HVAV and Hot Water Heater! Step inside to discover a home that seamlessly blends the best of the past with modern updates. The spacious eat-in-kitchen is perfect for cozy family gatherings and entertaining friends. With four bedrooms, there's room for everyone, and the updated bathroom ensures your comfort and convenience. What sets this property apart are the delightful details that harken back to a bygone era. You'll appreciate the dining room, featuring classic charm, and not one but two stairways leading to the second level. Imagine relaxing on your private balcony off the Master Bedroom or hosting outdoor get-togethers on your inviting deck. Convenience is key, with off-street parking making life a breeze. Plus, the home boasts new vinyl siding, providing a refreshed and well-kept exterior. But the real standout feature here is the gorgeous, real hardwood floors that add warmth and character to every room. This home is perfectly situated close to all conveniences, making your daily routines and errands a breeze. It's a unique chance to own a piece of York Suburban's heritage.
